
Sceario 1
Patient: “Alexa, open home ai”
Alexa: “Hi! I’m your home AI assistant. How can I help you?”
Patient: “I’m tired and want to go to bed”
Alexa: “I’ll help you get ready for bed. Should I dim the lights and lock the doors?”
Patient: “Yes please”
Alexa: “Done. Lights dimmed and all doors locked. Want me to adjust the thermostat for sleeping?”
Patient: “Yes, make it cooler”
Alexa: “I’ve set it to 68 degrees. Anything else?”
Patient: “No, that’s all”
Alexa: “Goodnight! Sleep well.”

Scenario 2

Patient: “Alexa, open home ai”
Alexa: “Hi! I’m your home AI assistant. How can I help you?”
Patient: “I heard a noise outside”
Alexa: “Let me check the cameras… I see a raccoon near your trash cans. Nothing to worry about. Want me to turn on the outside lights to scare it away?”
Patient: “Yes and make sure all doors are locked”
Alexa: “Outside lights on. All doors are locked. You’re safe. Should I keep the lights on for a while?”
Patient: “Yes leave them on for 30 minutes”
Alexa: “I’ll turn them off in 30 minutes automatically. Anything else?”
Patient: “No I feel better now thanks”
Alexa: “Glad I could help. I’m here if you need me.”